		<p style="font-size:28px; font-weight:bold;"> Will this be carryout or delivery? </p>
		<input type="radio" style="width:15px; height:15px;" name="delivery_option" id="carry_out" value="carryout" required>
				<label for="carryout"> Carryout </label><br>
		<input type="radio" style="width:15px; height:15px;" name="delivery_option" id="no_dining_room" value="delivery">		
				<label for="delivery"> Delivery ($5.00 Fee) </label><br>
					
	</div> -->
</div><br>
